u.s. lard consumpt in februari u.s. factori usag of lard in the product of both edibl and ined product dure februari total 22.0 mln lb , vs a revis 20.2 mln lb in januari , accord to censu bureau figur . in the year-earli period , usag , which includ hydrogen veget and anim fat and other oil in process , amount to 31.4 mln lb . usag in februari compris 16.6 mln lb of edibl product and 5.4 mln lb of ined product . total lard usag in the 1986/87 market season , which began octob 1 , amount to 125.2 mln lb , vs 185.6 mln lb in the year-ago period .